                                                                                                                                                                                                     Kapil support for seniors
                      
	Mumbai: Former India all-rounder Kapil Dev on Monday hailed the contribution of the senior cricketers in the team and said they should be given the freedom to retire when they want.         
	The seniors have been put under a lot of pressure. We should not forget that they have served the country. Whenever they feel like retiring their decision should be welcomed, Kapil told reporters here. (PTI)                                                                                                                          
